    "popularFaqs": "Popular FAQs",
    "faqs": {
      "q1": "How do I reset my smart LED strip?",
      "a1": "Hold the power button on the controller for 10 seconds until the strip flashes red. This will reset all WiFi settings and return it to pairing mode.",
      "q2": "What is the lifespan of your LED bulbs?",
      "a2": "Our LED bulbs are rated for 25,000 to 50,000 hours of use depending on the model. That translates to approximately 10-20 years of typical household usage.",
      "q3": "Can I cut the LED strips to size?",
      "a3": "Yes! All our LED strips have clearly marked cut lines every 5cm. Simply use sharp scissors to cut along the designated marks. Make sure the strip is unpowered before cutting.",
      "q4": "How long does shipping usually take?",
      "a4": "Standard shipping takes 3-5 business days within the continental US. Express shipping (1-2 business days) is available at checkout for an additional fee. Free shipping on orders over $75.",
      "q5": "Do your outdoor LEDs work in extreme weather?",
      "a5": "Our outdoor-rated LED products carry an IP65 or IP67 rating, meaning they are fully protected against dust and water jets. They operate safely in temperatures from -20\u00b0F to 120\u00b0F."
    },
